msg: Partial cleanup of jdbcapi,jdbc4.DataSourceTest to use utility methods to obtain already configured data sources. The static database name field is not a correct approach since it will be set once when the class is loaded and thus incorrect if the test is executed in a decorator that changes then configuration. The utility methods return a correctly configured data source.
Clarify that the utility methods that return data sources return a new one.
